Package: YAPSA
Type: Package
Title: Yet Another Package for Signature Analysis 
Version: 1.13.1
Date: 2019-11-26
Author: Daniel Huebschmann, Lea Jopp-Saile, Zuguang Gu and Matthias Schlesner
Maintainer: Daniel Huebschmann <huebschmann.daniel@googlemail.com>
